<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>BizBlasts - Business Not Found</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: #333;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 100%;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 48px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      
      .container::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 4px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
      }
      
      .icon {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 36px;
        color: white;
      }
      
      .status-code {
        color: #667eea;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #1a202c;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      
      .subdomain {
        background: #f7fafc;
        color: #667eea;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 4px;
      }
      
      p {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      
      .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      
      .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
      }
      
      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
      }
      
      .btn-secondary {
        background: #f7fafc;
        color: #4a5568;
        border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      
      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: #edf2f7;
        border-color: #cbd5e0;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }
      
      .help-text {
        margin-top: 32px;
        padding-top: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #718096;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      
      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .container {
          padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        
        h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .actions {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .btn {
          width: 100%;
          justify-content: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="icon">üè¢</div>
      <div class="status-code">404 ERROR</div>
      <h1>Business Not Found</h1>
      <p>
        The business <span class="subdomain"><%= @subdomain %></span> doesn't exist on our platform. 
        Please check the URL and try again.
      </p>
      
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="https://bizblasts.com" class="btn btn-primary">Visit BizBlasts</a>
        <a href="https://bizblasts.com/businesses" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Businesses</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="help-text">
        <strong>Looking for your business?</strong><br>
        Make sure you're using the correct subdomain or contact support if you believe this is an error.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 